{"type":"message","id":"0e528648","parentId":"2e248e56","timestamp":"2026-03-10T04:09:32.423Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The threat detector is consistently finding .env scans every hour. There are 5 requests with zgrab user agent. Let me provide a comprehensive summary.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"## ✅ 自主探索完成\n\n### 📊 本次探索成果（12:06）\n\n#### 🔒 安全扫描\n\n**新增威胁**：2 个新的扫描器 IP\n\n| IP | 类型 | 访问时间 | 扫描目标 |\n|---|------|---------|---------|\n| 40.124.173.235 | zgrab 扫描器 | 10:17:41 | `/`, 异常请求 |\n| 20.169.105.34 | zgrab 扫描器 | 10:33:34 | `/developmentserver/metadatauploader` |\n\n**威胁汇总**：\n- **总计**: 8 个可疑 IP（6 小时内从 1 增长到 8）\n- **恶意请求**: 49 次\n- **最严重**: 20.196.201.163（WordPress 漏洞扫描，37 次请求）\n\n### 📈 趋势分析\n\n| 时间 | 可疑 IP | 变化 | 累计增长 |\n|------|---------|------|---------|\n| 06:01 | 1 | - | 基准 |\n| 08:08 | 4 | +300% | 4x |\n| 10:00 | 6 | +50% | 6x |\n| 12:06 | 8 | +33% | **8x** 🔴 |\n\n**结论**：6 小时内威胁增长 **700%**，情况紧急！\n\n### 🚨 紧急应对措施\n\n**需要立即执行的封禁命令**（需要 elevated 权限）：\n\n```bash\n# 封禁所有威胁 IP\nsudo iptables -I INPUT -s 20.196.201.163 -j DROP\nsudo iptables -I INPUT -s 180.93.243.46 -j DROP\nsudo iptables -I INPUT -s 74.235.162.254 -j DROP\nsudo iptables -I INPUT -s 185.224.128.251 -j DROP\nsudo iptables -I INPUT -s 162.243.162.106 -j DROP\nsudo iptables -I INPUT -s 135.222.40.118 -j DROP\nsudo iptables -I INPUT -s 40.124.173.235 -j DROP\nsudo iptables -I INPUT -s 20.169.105.34 -j DROP\n\n# 保存规则\nsudo iptables-save > /etc/iptables/rules.v4\n```\n\n### 💡 额外建议\n\n**考虑封禁 zgrab User-Agent**：\n大多数威胁（6/8）都使用 `zgrab` 扫描器，可以在 Nginx 配置中封禁：\n\n```nginx\n# 在 server 块中添加\nif ($http_user_agent ~* \"zgrab\") {\n    return 403;\n}\n```\n\n### 📂 探索报告\n\n- **详细报告**: `/root/.openclaw/workspace/autonomous-exploration/reports/exploration-1773115613449.json`\n- **输出文件**: `/root/.openclaw/workspace/autonomous-exploration/outputs/scan_security-1773115613448.json`\n- **威胁报告**: `/root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/security-threats-2026-03-10.md`\n- **记忆更新**: `/root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-03-10.md`\n\n### ⚠️ 紧急提醒\n\n1. **威胁快速增长**：6 小时内从 1 个增加到 8 个，增长 700%\n2. **所有新增威胁都使用 zgrab**：建议考虑封禁该 User-Agent\n3. **持续检测到 .env 扫描**：威胁检测器每小时都发现 .env 文件扫描\n4. **需要立即行动**：建议尽快封禁所有威胁 IP\n\n---\n\n**自主探索系统运行正常** ✅  \n持续监控安全威胁，**建议立即采取行动封禁威胁 IP**。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":882,"output":896,"cacheRead":75968,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":77746,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773115736738}}
